high_descs: Walk straight and then veer right to the nightstand in the corner.
Pick up the TV remote.
Turn around and walk to the left side of the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman on top of the credit card.
Walk straight ahead around the ottoman to the chair.
Pick up the remote on the chair.
Walk back to the other side of the ottoman.
Place the remote to the right of the first remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on an ottoman.

high_descs: walk forwards to the TV, then hang a right and walk forwards to the cabinet at the end of the room
grab the remote controller off of the cabinet
turn right and walk to the foot rest in front of the couch
place the remote control down on the foot rest
move forwards past the couch over to the black chair at the end of the rug
grab the remote controller off of the black chair
turn around and walk back over to the foot rest at the other end of the rug
place the remote controller down on the foot rest
anns.task_desc: place two remote controllers on top of the foot rest

high_descs: Move towards the dresser on the right.
Pick up the remote control on top of the dresser.
Head to the ottoman in the center of the room.
Place the remote on the ottoman.
Move towards the black arm chair on the other side of the ottoman.
Pick up the remote on the arm chair.
Move back to the other side of the ottoman.
Place remote next to the other one on top of the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Place two remote controls in the room on the ottoman next to each other.
